Jamie McGrath (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jamie_McGrath_(actor) 0 Jamie McGrath (10 December 1974 – 20 March 1998) was an Australian actor who is best known for his role on the Australian soap opera Neighbours as Gary Briggs (1993–1994). He also appeared briefly on Neighbours earlier as another character, Peter Banks during two episodes in 1992.
